results.name: Triangle T(n,k) read by rows, giving number of bipartite graphs with n nodes (n >= 0) and k edges (0 <= k <= floor(n/2*n/2)).
comment: The sum of the m-th row is the (m-1)-st member of A033995, number of bipartite graphs with n nodes.
reference: F. Harary and E. M. Palmer, Graphical Enumeration, Academic Press, New York / London, 1973.
link: P. Hanlon, The enumeration of bipartite graphs, Discrete Math. 28 (1979), 49-57.
Juergen Will, Rows 0 to 10 of triangle.
results.author: _Juergen Will_, Jan 07 2018
